title: Display AI-Generated Images in a Jupyter Notebook
author: Teri Eyenike
description: This tutorial explains one way to generate a custom and personalized image with words and then store it in Cloudinary.
cntitle: 在Jupyter Notebook中显示AI生成的图像
cndescription: 本教程介绍一种生成包含文字的自定义个性化图像并将其存储到 Cloudinary 的方法。
